*Dinobot growled as the Ark shook from Predacon fire, he snarled and walked 
towards the doors. If they wouldn't come to him he would come to them!
He hit the doors with his shoulder and scanned before they opened out to the 
battle field beyond, he sighted his target and walked through.
Dinobot aimed his rifle at Scourge (hope I spelled it right) as the doors 
closed behind him, this one would be the first to sample the explosive power 
of a reround laser-pulse rifle!
He snarled as he locked in on target and fired at Scourge's torso, a mirage 
of charges heading straight for the Predacon's chest-plate. It wasn't called 
a reround for nothing.
Dinobot knew that this weapon hadn't been dubbed laser-pulse for nothing 
either, once the charges came into contact with a solid mass they would 
explode with the force of a small techtonic explosion.
Mainly ripping a bot to peices!
He snarled, he had chosen well!*
